* Biomass settled himself and crossed his arms across his chest-plate as he 
keeps his eyes on Perndabot, a smile playing across his lips.
Nue'e looked from Perndabot to Biomass and back again, sighing and glancing 
over towards Swift, wondering what she thought of all this.
But Nue'e sucks her arms to her chest and closes her eyes in surprise when 
Supernova runs by her, looking at him but then jumping in surprise then all 
of the other Galactors run by her, hearing a whistle and knowing from 
instinkt what it meant.
Biomass returns Perndabot's glair, not moving from his spot but looking 
towards the new bots in the sceen as he hears one of them whistle at Nue'e, 
lifting a brow in her direction to see what her reaction to all this 
excitement was. And all he saw was a rather disturbed fembot.
He looked back to Perndabot, not even looking up as the Galactors come 
together but gives them a look that says" give me a break here!" when they 
offer to pound him into the dust if Perndabot failed.
Biomass then lifted a brow at Perndabot.*

" Your move."
